{"tid":516841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個人太負面真係唔適合拍拖","createTime":"2018-01-01T18:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:11:57.000Z","uid":73227,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9bd9f5a02b050f406e8c05344672968dfb4186","tid":516841,"uid":73227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"諗嘢太負面冇乜自信心成日都會覺得<br />\n咁辛苦建立一段感情 去到最後都係分手收場<br />\n你仲點會對下一段感情有信心？<br />\n你想認真唔代表人哋都想認真<br />\n到頭來比盡你咪幾年後又話淡咗<br />\n有幾多對情侶可以挨過呢一關<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實冇得到過就唔會有失去<br />\n細個覺得呢句野好on9<br />\n大概係你遇到一個好唔想放手又或者好驚失去嘅人 先會明呢句意思<br />\n我好垃圾 我承受唔住失去你嗰種痛"},{"pid":"56f93908f0f373e0bcc68a78bcc61477184b2c29","tid":516841,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"好攰"},{"pid":"537715082210335380c6e6f32c05d38732596dca","tid":516841,"uid":73227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"56f93908f0f373e0bcc68a78bcc61477184b2c29","tid":516841,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"好攰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"失去一個人 變到想單性繁殖 <br />\n一方面驚失去 <br />\n另一方面驚因爲驚失去比唔到好似以前咁多既愛佢"},{"pid":"bcf4dc560a7a8cb205a51d3c326580bbb03a86de","tid":516841,"uid":123650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:15:52.000Z","msg":"我男友都好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最衰佢個仆街ex搞到佢唔信人"},{"pid":"71f20eaa7d1d977491899e965edb7ca45d56e596","tid":516841,"uid":73227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bcf4dc560a7a8cb205a51d3c326580bbb03a86de","tid":516841,"uid":123650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:15:52.000Z","msg":"我男友都好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最衰佢個仆街ex搞到佢唔信人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20